[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    617[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    618[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## Estimated Implementation Time
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    619[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    620[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | Tier | Timeline | What You Get |
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    621[0m:[38;5;10m[49m |------|----------|--------------|
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    622[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | **Basic** | 4-6 weeks | Entity extraction + rule-based relation detection + DynamoDB storage. Single-note processing, no aggregation. Manual review of all detections. |
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    623[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | **Production-ready** | 10-14 weeks | Full pipeline with assertion filtering, severity classification, expected-effects filtering, real-time alerting for high-severity events, and basic batch aggregation. Tuned false positive rate to <25%. |
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    624[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | **With variations** | 16-22 weeks | Cross-note temporal reasoning, Neptune-based signal detection with disproportionality analysis, integration with medication reconciliation, patient-reported data ingestion, and safety dashboard. |
